       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    ARI66308.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA ARI66308.
      *
      *     Eliminar registo de documento e documento
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE ARI66308         '.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE ARCD4102 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY ARCV6630.
       COPY ARCV6631.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY ARCK0001.
       COPY ARCK0002.
       COPY ETCL0002.
       COPY ARCL7025.
      *
      *COPY ARCL0400.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-ARVT4102                 PIC  X(08) VALUE 'ARVT4102'.
           05 IND-NZSEQ                    PIC S9(04) BINARY.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            VARIAVEIS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-CNISERIES                 PIC  X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CBIBLI                    PIC  X(10) VALUE SPACES.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME                  PIC  X(08) VALUE 'ARI66308'.
           05 WS-INDICATOR                 PIC S9(04) BINARY.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE ARI66308         '.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO ARCV6630-MSG.
           MOVE ARCV6630-ASE               TO ARCV6631-ASE.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA'    TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE ARCV6630-ADE               TO ARCV6631-ADE.
      *
           PERFORM 2100-VALIDACOES
              THRU 2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
      *

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2300-APAGA-DOC
                 THRU 2300-APAGA-DOC-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-APAGAR-DADOS
                 THRU 2299-APAGAR-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-VALIDACOES.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-VALIDACOES'       TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE ARCV6630-CCHAVE            TO ARCD4102-CCHAVE.
           MOVE ARCV6630-ZSEQ              TO ARCD4102-ZSEQ.
      *
           EXEC SQL
              SELECT CNORIG
                   , CNISERIES
                   , CBIBLI
                INTO :ARCD4102-CNORIG
                   , :ARCD4102-CNISERIES
                   , :ARCD4102-CBIBLI
                FROM ARVT4102
               WHERE CCHAVE  =  :ARCD4102-CCHAVE
                 AND ZSEQ    =  :ARCD4102-ZSEQ
           END-EXEC.
      *
           MOVE CON-ARVT4102               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
           EVALUATE TRUE
              WHEN DB2-OK
                 MOVE ARCD4102-CNISERIES TO WS-CNISERIES
                 MOVE ARCD4102-CBIBLI    TO WS-CBIBLI
              WHEN DB2-NOTFND
              WHEN NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                                           TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                           TO ARCV6631-CCHAVE-S
                 MOVE ARCK0001-CCHAVE-N-EXISTS
                                           TO ARCV6631-CCHAVE-MSG
                 MOVE ARCK0002-CAPLIC-AR   TO ARCV6631-CCHAVE-CAPLIC
           END-EVALUATE.
      *
       2199-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2200-APAGAR-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-APAGAR-DADOS.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2200-APAGAR-DADOS'     TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE ARCV6630-CCHAVE            TO ARCD4102-CCHAVE.
           MOVE ARCV6630-ZSEQ              TO ARCD4102-ZSEQ.
      *
           EXEC SQL
              DELETE
                FROM ARVT4102
               WHERE CCHAVE  =  :ARCD4102-CCHAVE
                 AND ZSEQ    =  :ARCD4102-ZSEQ
           END-EXEC.
      *
           MOVE CON-ARVT4102               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
           EVALUATE TRUE
              WHEN DB2-OK
                 CONTINUE
              WHEN DB2-NOTFND
              WHEN NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                                           TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                           TO ARCV6631-CCHAVE-S
                 MOVE ARCK0001-CCHAVE-N-EXISTS
                                           TO ARCV6631-CCHAVE-MSG
                 MOVE ARCK0002-CAPLIC-AR   TO ARCV6631-CCHAVE-CAPLIC
           END-EVALUATE.
      *
       2299-APAGAR-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      * 2300 APAGA DOCUMENTO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2300-APAGA-DOC.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2300-APAGA-DOC   '     TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           SET  ARCL7025-RCODE-OK           TO TRUE.
           MOVE WS-CBIBLI                   TO ARCL7025-BIBLI.
           MOVE WS-CNISERIES                TO ARCL7025-FILEN.

      * Executa CLP para apagar o ficheiro do documento
           PERFORM CALL-ARM70025
              THRU CALL-ARM70025-EXIT.

           IF NOT ARCL7025-RCODE-OK
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                                           TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                           TO ARCV6631-CCHAVE-S
                 MOVE ARCK0001-DOC-NAO-DEL
                                           TO ARCV6631-CCHAVE-MSG
                 MOVE ARCK0002-CAPLIC-AR   TO ARCV6631-CCHAVE-CAPLIC
           END-IF.
      *
       2300-APAGA-DOC-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA'   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'VIAL0002-IND-ERROS   ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM (1)
              MOVE  VIAL0002-IND-ERROS     TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE ARCV6631-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE ARCV6631-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE ARCV6631-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.
      *
       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0016.
           COPY ARCP7025.
      *
